"within a few seconds and with no downtime without needing a central SAN, as "
"the data is already replicated to multiple nodes."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ===
#: UG9/en/linstor-proxmox.adoc:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "Upgrading Proxmox"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
